{"tid":1574992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[二手/ 冇圖] 星期日有警狗槍實彈槍向示威者","createTime":"2019-09-16T16:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:06:49.000Z","uid":296231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85c71c9131156b9aeb34522d470b068478b25598","tid":1574992,"uid":296231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:02:14.000Z","msg":"今日同阿媽傾電話，佢竟然冇不反對通知書都有出去，好感動！！<br />\n阿媽話佢唔算早去，到金鐘果陣差唔多５點<br />\n突然有唔知邊個議員衝出黎話政總開左波，<br />\n叫冇GEAR既快Ｄ向灣仔方向走。<br />\n阿媽就走左去告士打道諗住睇下有冇巴士搭，<br />\n成條街都冇咩人，離遠見到２隻交警狗係馬路，<br />\n之後見到４，５個街口外，<br />\n突然７，８個黑衫勇武係小路到衝左出黎，<br />\n打９果２隻警狗。<br />\n後來有隻交警狗黎増援，<br />\n一落車即刻ＭＵＮ槍指住班勇武。<br />\n班勇武打完快閃安全撤退。<br />\n阿媽話冇咩人，又冇記者。<br />\n不過佢比隻狗嚇死，佢話隻狗水平咁舉槍，亂９咁射真係會射死人。<br />\n<br />\n唔知阿媽有冇睇錯。<br />\n<br />\n真係多謝班勇武，<br />\n我阿媽有Ｄ年紀了，不過佢核爆都唔割！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b49d1724845ab93c271462f1b927460e65bae53","tid":1574992,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:02:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b51b0bb6157044fa57186e45ea6fbe69dfae3bd","tid":1574992,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"915國旗行動好成功!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jR5wr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jR5wr1.jpg&h=d9b2c693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbd9aa57be596c96f31e7dc3cf49f0ed4dd72026","tid":1574992,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[重開][品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574973</a>"},{"pid":"857fe05645568